. So her later public career as a novelist had been given some very personal preparation.</p>","shortUrl":"http://gu.com/p/4ht7g","wordcount":"176","thumbnail":"http://media.guim.co.uk/93ad9c7f55d9d5fe9c92c7d2debe88cc21aac0b3/46_567_1830_1097/140.jpg"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/books/2016/mar/15/tim-hilton-on-anita-brookner-obituary","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/books/2016/mar/15/tim-hilton-on-anita-brookner-obituary","sectionName":"Books","elements":[{"id":"93ad9c7f55d9d5fe9c92c7d2debe88cc21aac0b3","relation":"main","type":"image","assets":[{"type":"image","file":"http://media.guim.co.uk/93ad9c7f55d9d5fe9c92c7d2debe88cc21aac0b3/46_567_1830_1097/1000.jpg","typeData":{"copyright":"Copyright (c) 1995 Rex Features. No use without permission.","mediaApiUri":"https://api.media.gutools.co.uk/images/93ad9c7f55d9d5fe9c92c7d2debe88cc21aac0b3","suppliersReference":"238850ab","altText":"Anita Brookner in 1995.","caption":"Anita Brookner in 1995.","source":"Julian Calder/Rex/Shutterstock","credit":"Photograph: Julian Calder/Rex/Shutterstock","mediaId":"93ad9c7f55d9d5fe9c92c7d2debe88cc21aac0b3","displayCredit":"true","imageType":"Photograph","secureFile":"https://media.guim.co.uk/93ad9c7f55d9d5fe9c92c7d2debe88cc21aac0b3/46_567_1830_1097/1000.jpg","width":"1000","height":"599"},"mimeType":"image/jpeg"},{"type":"image","file":"http://media.guim.co.uk/93ad9c7f55d9d5fe9c92c7d2debe88cc21aac0b3/46_567_1830_1097/500.jpg","typeData":{"copyright":"Copyright (c) 1995 Rex Features. No use without permission.","mediaApiUri":"https://api.media.gutools.co.uk/images/93ad9c7f55d9d5fe9c92c7d2debe88cc21aac0b3","suppliersReference":"238850ab","altText":"Anita Brookner in 1995.","caption":"Anita Brookner in 1995.","source":"Julian Calder/Rex/Shutterstock","credit":"Photograph: Julian Calder/Rex/Shutterstock","mediaId":"93ad9c7f55d9d5fe9c92c7d2debe88cc21aac0b3","displayCredit":"true","imageType":"Photograph","secureFile":"https://media.guim.co.uk/93ad9c7f55d9d5fe9c92c7d2debe8